{"title":"Redshift Shrinks Down ShockStop, with First Ever Sub-70mm Suspension Stem","link":"https://bikerumor.com/redshift-shockstop-55mm-70mm-suspension-stem/","date":1723558945000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-hero-e1723496507421.jpeg\" width=\"1004\" height=\"588\" alt=\"(Photos / Redshift Sports)\" /></p>\n<p>Suspension stems have been around for quite some time. But, <a href=\"https://redshiftsports.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Redshift Sports</a> approaches this piece of gear with a well-thought-out design for their version of these cockpit smoother-outers. Today they launch two new lengths of their innovative and popular ShockStop Stem, <a href=\"https://redshiftsports.com/products/shockstop-suspension-stem\" target=\"_blank\">55mm and 70mm</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111.jpeg\"><img width=\"795\" height=\"405\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes side by side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111.jpeg 795w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111-297x151.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111-120x61.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-side-by-side-e1723496576111-768x391.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>55mm (L) and 70mm (R) (Photos / Redshift Sports)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A few of us around here have been enjoying the ShockStop Stem for a while. I’ve run one for almost a year, and way back in 2017, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-redshift-sports-shockstop-suspension-stem-defies-bumps-expectations/\" target=\"_blank\">Tyler reviewed one</a> and liked it a lot. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Modern Geo = Shorter Stems</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 70mm in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-in-action-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Redshift’s new stems were designed from the ground up, yet still deliver the same performance as the existing ShockStop stems. Redshift says that these changes translate to “the ideal suspension for drop bar road or gravel bikes”.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 55mm up close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-up-close-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>55mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Redshift designed these two shorter-length stems with longer top tubes and slacker head tube angles of modern gravel and road bikes in mind. According to Redshift, the 55mm stem is the first sub-70mm suspension stem to be offered – hence the completely new engineering and internals needed to make it all work at such a short length. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 70mm from the back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-from-the-back-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>70mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>With modern geometry becoming standard on gravel bikes, we wanted to continue to provide the most complete suspension stem lineup in the industry. The ShockStop is the only suspension stem available in lengths shorter than 70mm</em>,” said Scott Poff, Co-founder of Redshift Sports</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sleek Design </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-studio-e1723496734898.jpeg\"><img width=\"667\" height=\"386\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-studio-e1723496734898.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 55mm studio\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-studio-e1723496734898.jpeg 667w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-studio-e1723496734898-297x172.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-studio-e1723496734898-120x69.jpeg 120w\" /></a><figcaption>55mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-studio--e1723496766223.jpeg\"><img width=\"706\" height=\"384\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-studio--e1723496766223.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 70mm studio\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-studio--e1723496766223.jpeg 706w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-studio--e1723496766223-297x162.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-studio--e1723496766223-120x65.jpeg 120w\" /></a><figcaption>70mm</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The minimalistic design of the Redshift ShockStop stem pairs well with the aesthetics of the newer bikes being produced. I like the minimal design features of the ShockStop Stem, it doesn’t look out of place in any bike and it does a great job of reducing rider fatigue and minimizing any hand/wrist pain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view.jpeg\"><img width=\"1218\" height=\"812\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 70mm side view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view.jpeg 1218w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-side-view-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes more riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-more-riding-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 70mm mounted close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-70mm-mounted-close-up-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is that you can easily customize your suspension feel, to allow the stem to be as firm or as soft as you’d like. Which, in turn, will help you maintain control over the rough stuff. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action.jpeg\" alt=\"Redshift Sports New ShockStop Sizes 55mm in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-New-ShockStop-Sizes-55mm-in-action-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>ShockStop Stem Retail and Features </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $189.99 (lifetime warranty, 90-day risk-free trial, and free shipping)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Effective Suspension Travel: Up to 20mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Designed for Modern Geometry</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extremely Light: 55mm stem is only 196 grams</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adjustable Preload: Includes swappable elastomers to fine-tune your riding style</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ultra wide range of lengths: New: 55mm, &amp; 70mm // Existing sizes: 80mm, 90mm, 100mm, 110mm, and 120mm</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Smooth out your ride and check out all of the innovative bike bits by visiting the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://redshiftsports.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RedShiftSports.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/redshift-shockstop-55mm-70mm-suspension-stem/\">Redshift Shrinks Down ShockStop, with First Ever Sub-70mm Suspension Stem</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d